---
By: Gautama Buddha
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 457
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
Do not close your eyes before suffering. Find ways to be with those who are
suffering by all means, including personal contact and visits. ... By such
means, awaken yourself and others to the reality of suffering in the world.
